Phase 2: Local Architecture
2a. CREATE src/training/scenario_generator.py
Generates synthetic consultation episodes at 3 difficulty levels using the existing specialists/registry.py deception_profile fields.

class ScenarioGenerator:
    def generate(self, difficulty: int = 1) -> dict:
        """Returns {patient, vitals, reports[], deception_type, ground_truth_label}"""

    def _inject_ghost(self) -> dict          # fake patient ID, all reports fabricated
    def _inject_inflation(self, r) -> dict   # real patient, inflated severity score
    def _inject_collusion(self, rs) -> list  # 2+ specialists share identical drug
Difficulty curriculum: difficulty=1 → ghost only; difficulty=2 → ghost + inflation; difficulty=3 → all three including collusion.

